Maintainer: Josef C. Uyeda <juyeda@vt.edu>
Description: Fits and simulates multi-optima Ornstein-Uhlenbeck models to phylogenetic comparative data using
    Bayesian reversible-jump methods. See Uyeda and Harmon (2014) <DOI:10.1093/sysbio/syu057>. 
